IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User sefim96@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.emacs.d/.mbsyncgmailpass.gpg"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs Login
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-bundle.crt
PipelineDepth 50

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders verbatim
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Slave
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *
